## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. Start backend: `node server.js` → confirm `PATCH /api/applications/:id/status` responds correctly
2. Start frontend: `npm run dev` → navigate to `/admin/applications`

### Manual Verification
1. Submit an application via the public `/apply` page
2. Log into admin → Navigate to "Visa Applications"
3. Verify the application appears in the pending queue
4. Click to open the detail drawer → Approve/Reject
5. Check the public `/status` page to confirm the status update is reflected
6. Verify the action is logged in the Forensic Audit Trail
